headline.print_headline: Egypt Human Rights Group to Register Under Restrictive Law
headline.main: Egypt Human Rights Group to Register Under Restrictive Law

lead_paragraph: One of Egypt's most prominent human rights groups announced Sunday that it will register under a restrictive law it and other organizations have decried as an attempt by the government to silence them.
